<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 03:11:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>越南与菲律宾签署南海安全协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-philippines-seal-deals-south-china-sea-security-2024-01-30/</link><description>越南和菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯在进行国事访问期间宣布，越南和菲律宾周二同意加强两国海岸警卫队之间的合作，防止南海发生不愉快的事件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 02:54:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-philippines-seal-deals-south-china-sea-security-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>由于对中国房地产业的担忧重压，亚洲股市下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-30/</link><description>亚洲股市周二下跌，受法院下令清算房地产巨头中国恒大的影响，而地缘政治紧张局势加剧支撑了油价，并在美联储会议之前抑制了风险偏好</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 02:47:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>香港领导人开始推动立法以收紧国家安全法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-leaders-start-legislative-push-tighten-national-security-laws-2024-01-30/</link><description>香港领导人周二证实，他打算在北京于 2020 年对香港实施的全面立法的基础上尽快通过新的国家安全法，并表示香港有宪法责任实施新法律。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 02:18:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-leaders-start-legislative-push-tighten-national-security-laws-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>2023 年丰田继续稳坐全球最畅销汽车制造商宝座</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-keeps-crown-worlds-top-selling-automaker-2023-2024-01-30/</link><description>丰田汽车周二表示，2023 年销量达到创纪录的 1120 万辆，连续第四年成为全球最畅销汽车制造商。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 02:07:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-keeps-crown-worlds-top-selling-automaker-2023-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>独家：伦敦金属交易所瞄准香港作为仓库扩张的选择</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lme-targets-hong-kong-option-warehouse-expansion-2024-01-30/</link><description>五位知情人士表示，伦敦金属交易所（LME）正在研究将香港作为扩大其全球金属仓库网络的地点，希望香港的成功可能为其最终目标中国大陆打开大门。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 01:02:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lme-targets-hong-kong-option-warehouse-expansion-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，美国禁用了针对关键基础设施的中国黑客网络</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-disabled-chinese-hacking-network-targeting-critical-infrastructure-sources-2024-01-29/</link><description>据两名西方安全官员和一名知情人士透露，美国政府近几个月发起了一项行动，打击普遍存在的中国黑客行动，该行动成功破坏了数千台互联网连接设备。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 23:09:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-disabled-chinese-hacking-network-targeting-critical-infrastructure-sources-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>由于美国出口管制，泰瑞达从中国撤回了价值 10 亿美元的制造业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/teradyne-pulled-1-billion-worth-manufacturing-china-amid-us-export-controls-2024-01-29/</link><description>泰瑞达发言人周一表示，在美国出口法规导致供应链中断后，半导体测试设备供应商泰瑞达去年将价值约 10 亿美元的制造业从中国撤出。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 22:36:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/teradyne-pulled-1-billion-worth-manufacturing-china-amid-us-export-controls-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>年度预测低于预期 惠而浦股价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/whirlpool-shares-slip-after-weaker-than-expected-annual-forecasts-2024-01-29/</link><description>惠而浦周一预计全年销售额和利润将低于分析师的预期，因这家家电制造商面临来自竞争对手的定价压力和更高的费用，导致其股价在盘后交易中下跌约 4%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 22:13:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/whirlpool-shares-slip-after-weaker-than-expected-annual-forecasts-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：忘掉中国过度建设的后果吧——这是就业、就业和美联储</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-29/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 21:47:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>一名女子因涉嫌从中国欺诈中洗钱 63 亿美元而在伦敦受审</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/woman-tried-london-over-alleged-bitcoin-laundering-63-bln-china-fraud-2024-01-29/</link><description>检察官周一告诉伦敦一家法院，一名女子将比特币兑换成现金和财产，以帮助洗钱在中国实施的 50 亿英镑（63 亿美元）欺诈案的收益。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 18:03:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/woman-tried-london-over-alleged-bitcoin-laundering-63-bln-china-fraud-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>议员们希望美国调查四家参与福特电池厂的中国公司——信函</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/lawmakers-want-us-probe-four-chinese-firms-involved-ford-battery-plant-letter-2024-01-29/</link><description>据路透社周一看到的一封信函，美国众议院两个委员会的主席要求拜登政府调查四家中国公司，他们称这些公司参与了福特汽车计划中的密歇根电池工厂。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 17:38:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/lawmakers-want-us-probe-four-chinese-firms-involved-ford-battery-plant-letter-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国副总理敦促在市场暴跌之际加大对上市公司的支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-vice-premier-urges-more-support-listed-firms-amid-market-rout-2024-01-29/</link><description>据新华社报道，在股市持续暴跌之际，中国国务院副总理何立峰周一呼吁加大对上市公司的支持，以帮助稳定资本市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 11:49:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-vice-premier-urges-more-support-listed-firms-amid-market-rout-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国护照持有者可以免签前往哪些国家？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/which-countries-can-chinese-passport-holders-visit-without-visa-2024-01-29/</link><description>中国因新冠肺炎 (COVID-19) 自我隔离三年，并于 2023 年重新开放边境，并与部分国家签署了免签证协议，以鼓励其公民旅行，这对吸引中国游客的外国目的地来说是一个福音。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:30:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/which-countries-can-chinese-passport-holders-visit-without-visa-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大承认香港法院的清算令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrande-acknowledges-hk-court-order-liquidate-2024-01-29/</link><description>中国恒大周一承认，香港法院下令对这家全球负债最重的房地产开发商进行清算，原因是该公司在拖欠债券两年多后未能提供具体的重组计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:09:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrande-acknowledges-hk-court-order-liquidate-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>对冲资金流 对冲基金以五年来最快速度买入中国股票 - 高盛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-hedge-funds-lap-up-china-stocks-fastest-pace-5-years-goldman-2024-01-29/</link><description>高盛在给客户的一份报告中写道，对冲基金上周三天内以五年多来最快的速度抢购遭受重创的中国股票。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:06:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-hedge-funds-lap-up-china-stocks-fastest-pace-5-years-goldman-2024-01-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>